{"word":"ἐξευρίσκω","slug":"ἐξευρίσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξευρίσκω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ευρήσω</el>) (aor2 <el>-εῦρον</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to find out, discover</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to invent</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>simply <i>to find</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><i>to seek out, search after</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>5. </b><i>to find out, win, get, procure</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}